We get 500 in our pocket for our budget.
We put slippers on our foot to walk outside.
We went to the market for buying some ingredients.
We ask the vendors to get some discount for the ingredients;
1 kilo of Pork,Kangkong,Tomato,Garlic,Onion,Sinigang Mix,Labanos
1 kilo of Chicken wings,crispy fry chicken,Oil
1 kilo of Galunggong,Crispy fry fish,Oil
Then after we bought some ingrdients we go home
We remove our slippers and come inside the kitchen
Then we check our budget if there's amount that is left
Lastly, we cooked all the food we bought in the market.

